      = 1 + c * (2 * size c + 160 * MAX 1 k ** 2 * size k * size c * size n ** 4)  by hop_1_n
      = 1 + 2 * c * size c + 160 * c * MAX 1 k ** 2 * size k * size c * size n ** 4
