  `body x <= 2 * size x + stepsOf (poly_introM n k x)` by rw[Abbr`body`] >>
  `stepsOf (poly_introM n k x) <= 160 * MAX 1 k ** 2 * size k * size x * size n ** 4` by rw[poly_introM_steps_bound] >>
